Babuine Component Model
========================

The babuine component model intends create quickly and easily software
components.

The framework contains the following features:

	* Inversion of Control / Dependency Injection framework.
	* Simple.
	* Non-intrusive framework code.
	* Fast.
	* Frienldy with .NET namings and conventions.

* Requeriments and Compiling:
	
	* You will need NAnt 0.85
	* You will need NUnit 2.2.8

	Just type nant.

* Breaking change:

	Well, for the new 0.4.6 version, is the first including a big philosophy
	change.  The change is the switch to a IoC philosophy instead of the
	Service Locator one.
